Always Armed					KEY:Herald ~ Always Armed					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural							DESC:Heralds can summon their signature weapon as a standard action. If its herald doesn't have a signature weapon, it can summon any nonmagical weapon as a standard action (including special materials); the weapon disappears if it leaves the herald's grasp.
